  "text": "6. q-ary Robust Positioning Sequences. In this section, we modify the construction of Berkowitz and Kopparty and give a new class of q-ary positioning sequences robust to a constant fraction of errors. We first review Berkowitz and Kopparty's work. Theorem 6.1 (Berkowitz and Kopparty [CITATION_1] ). Fix a generator g of F * q . Let G = (σ σ σ 0 , σ σ σ 1 , . . . , σ σ σ q k −1 ) be a (k, q)-Gray code. For each σ σ σ i , let f i (x) ∈ F q [x] be the unique interpolating polynomial of degree k + 1 so that",
